	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要給我一點時間，<delay8 />
我就會恢復正常了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以在我拿出氣勢前，<delay8 />先讓我獨處吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很難<delay8 />
盡如人意呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然<delay frames="5" />出發點是好的，<delay20 />
