<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的會讓人無言以對呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我為什麼做事<delay20 />
就是這麼粗心大意呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我之前做了<delay8 /><tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />卻說<delay8 />
有<tag a="135" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的味道<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原本想說可以襯出食材的味道，<delay20 />
我才會加了不少東西進去，<delay8 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以這樣做不行嗎<tag a="110" b="0" />？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不用太在意啦</message>
	<message label="103_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這確實不太好</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道<delay20 />你在安慰我嗎？<delay frames="30" />
